---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the CTAI website."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-ink-200 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-ink-300 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">What We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it. The only
          personal data we store is the contact information (email address) of users who choose
          to sign up for notifications about new content or features.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">How We Use It</h2>
        <p>
          Email addresses are used solely to send occasional updates about new site content,
          features, or improvements. We do not sell, share, or provide your information to
          any third party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Opting Out</h2>
        <p>
          You may opt out of all communications at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link
          in any email, or by contacting us at
          <a href="mailto:chadananda@gmail.com" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">chadananda@gmail.com</a>.
          Upon request, we will delete your email address from our records.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Cookies & Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          This site uses a service worker for font caching to improve performance. We use
          PostHog for anonymous, privacy-focused analytics to understand how the site is used
          and to improve the experience. PostHog may set cookies to distinguish unique visitors.
          No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          The site is hosted on Cloudflare. Images may be served via Imgix. Neither service
          receives personal data from this site beyond standard HTTP request information
          (IP address, user agent) inherent to web browsing.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
